welcome_message_body: Welcome to Fleming Island! Known for its charming small-town feel and beautiful natural landscapes, we are excited for you to explore and experience all that our city has to offer. Enjoy your stay and make the most of your time here!

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Jacksonville NAS Airport handles all commercial flights and is equipped with modern amenities.

terminals.name: Military Terminal
terminals.description: The military terminal at Jacksonville NAS Airport serves the needs of the Naval Air Station and is not open to the public.

wifi.note: Complimentary WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at St Augustine Airport serves domestic flights and offers various amenities for travelers.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Jacksonville Airport serves domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Concourse A
terminals.description: Concourse A at Jacksonville Airport serves mainly domestic flights.

terminals.name: Concourse B
terminals.description: Concourse B at Jacksonville Airport serves mostly international flights.

wifi.note: Free wifi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Craig Municipal Airport serves all commercial and private flights.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: The private terminal at Craig Municipal Airport is reserved for private and charter flights.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.
